<plot>In a bleak, not-to-distant future, a lone man finds himself confronted on all sides by warring political factions, conspiracy theorists and all manner of people who try to influence his life. Not wanting to take a stance, but with an equal desire not to fade into obscurity, our main character responds to these pressures in the only way he knows how--he rides his bicycle. Experience thrills, excitement, and a man dressed in a garbage bag as one man's bike-ride takes him to all corners of the globe on a quest for self-discovery in a world that has lost itself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?217691</url></doc>
